\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10631877 MJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 
Yes. He used to read to us. And Katie, Katie used to read to us. My mother and father used to go out you see. They would go out for an evening perhaps somew
here you know what I mean. And Katie would be with us and she'd read the Bears and all that. She would have us on her lap and she used to sing "What a friend we have in Jesus". She used to sing. I remember it so well you know. Teach one of us and then per
haps she would go down on the floor and we would be on her back. That was lovely. Um yes.
