Well I don't know I'm sure. I - I can't say why. But there is a meaning isn't there for a Liberal isn't there. And of course when - when - the Liberals - they went didn't they become the Labour when -
 Tom Griffiths in Pontypool. Tom Griffiths I think it was, yes. But he didn't do much in politics. They don't in business you know. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1924861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 What about your mother, did she take an interest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10631877 MJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1924861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 Do you know what her views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10631877 MJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 Same as my - my father's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1924861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 Why do you think she held those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10631877 MJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 I couldn't say love.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1924861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 Can you remember your father or mother voting in a general election before 1919?
