\insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 lection. Mm. I don't remember them voting. My father must have done though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1924861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 Would you know what party he voted for?
