 married in the August - August 1925. And my mother had been ill you see in fact she died. And our wedding was put off until - Boxing Day, 1925. It was put off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1924861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 So you had a bit of an upset really?
