\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1924861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 Did they make a certain time to come in at night or anything like that, were they more strict or less strict after you decided to get marrie
d?
