\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10631877 MJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 Oh you see, we buried my mother look and we lived there with my father. Lived there with my father.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1924861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 Did you buy any household equipment before your marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10631877 MJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 No.
