\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1924861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 Can you remember exactly what you wore?
