Grey. Grey dress, yes, and a grey coat. I've got a photo here somewhere. And a black - a hat I made myself, I made the hat myself. Of - georgette. Black georgette, and my - little flowers right across the front,
 and it - it - you know, - they dipped down those days, you know, big hat - dipped down. Oh and I had a big - grey fur, and a grey coat, it was a coat and dress.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1924861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 You picked grey did you?
