Well - what's the colour of the suit now - he had - it was a most unusual colour, it wasn't brown. It was more like that - that there, that colour. And - a trilby of course, a nice new trilby as well you know, oh yes, he looked very nice, smart
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1924861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13768631\charrsid810411 Did you wear something old, something new, something borrowed, something blue?
